text:
this game simply made me fall in love with it.
-stunning sceneries;
-"i wont move or start bc i want to listen to the soundtrack" kind of soundtrack;
-characters with whom you create emotional ties and for whom you wish they were happy;
-very interesting story.
if you like point and click games with an intriguing storyline, challenging puzzles and to have your feelings crushed at given moments, this is a game for you (+the first syberia)

+ improved controls over Syberia;
+ still has the amazing art style and soundtrack;
+ new and old characters to interact with;
+ the story is still enchanting and full of surprises;
- locations feel like they have less variety now.
Recommended.

+ visually stunning with its art style;
+ gorgeous music;
+ memorable characters;
+ challenging puzzles;
- a bit short.
An experience like no others. Recommended, no questions.
